– ESG criteria are included in the compensation system for members of the Managing Board and senior managers

At Siemens, sustainability is rooted in all that we do, includ- ing our business purpose and strategy, corporate culture, processes, and guidelines. The management of sustainability matters is embedded across our Siemens businesses, Service and Governance units, and countries. Sustainability has also been an integral component of management compensation since fiscal 2020. Put simply, we strive to make sustainability everyone’s responsibility at Siemens.